'''Iv<U+00E1>n Gonzalo Bella ''' (born 13 September 1989 in [[Buenos Aires]]) is an [[Argentina|Argentine]] [[Association football|football]] midfielder who plays for [[Club Atl<U+00E9>tico V<U+00E9>lez S<U+00E1>rsfield|V<U+00E9>lez S<U+00E1>rsfield]].

Bella made his league debut in a 0-0 draw against Independiente on 8 June 2008.

In January 2009 Bella was selected to join the [[Argentina U-20|Argentina under-20]] squad for the [[2009 South American Youth Championship]] in [[Venezuela]]. 
 
